 3- yạ sạỷrạaⁿ fy sẖʿạb ạldrwb rfqạaⁿ bḍʿfy wqlby ạlkỷyb
 ạ̹n knt ạ̉nt ạ̉kẖdẖt ḥbyby ql ly wḍʿth fy ạ̉y ṣwb
 4- yạ mrym ạ̹ltfty wạnẓryny qfy bʿydạaⁿ wlạ tlmsyny
